      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, the unit has been subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure peak operational standards. The cabin remains refined and the exterior retains a commanding presence, making this an exemplary choice for those seeking reliability and sophistication. This offering is a testament to disciplined ownership and professional care.",
      "price": 36500.0,
