    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still has plenty of life left in it? I'm selling my car, and it's honestly been such a gem. It runs beautifully and has been kept in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love here and there, but it\u2019s super clean and ready to hit the road today. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
