    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example features a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Significant preventative maintenance has been completed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the platform. The chassis remains taut with refreshed suspension bushings, maintaining the communicative handling characteristics this generation is known for. A prime candidate for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience without the premium of a collector-grade garage queen.",
